  "description": "¶Preparation (Traditional) Construct the ritual circle, inscribed with divine names (typically in Latin or Hebrew transliteration).\nPrepare the Triangle of Art for the spirit to appear within.\nHave the Seal of Buer ready, either worn on your person (as a ring or medallion) or displayed within the triangle.\nPrepare incense (typically frankincense or a Mars-aligned mixture).\nTools include: sword or wand, consecrated parchment, ritual garments, and a book or document to receive the spirit’s answers.\n",
